{"tid":2331946,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"心入面總有個位置留比佢","createTime":"2020-12-19T08:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T09:29:44.000Z","uid":137043,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aab246d8691f0bc8ab807973bb13d4935bf4046c","tid":2331946,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"見感情台有巴打講起「介唔介意另一半最愛嘅唔係你」<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況的確有，但我諗更多人係心中永遠有個位留比好特別嘅嗰個人。未必係一齊過，可能只係暗戀過、曖昧過、甚至差少少一齊。<br />\n<br />\n就因為咁先更加深印象，大個之後回想返先發現當時自己做錯決定：「點解嗰陣唔發覺？點解嗰陣會唔夠膽？咁明顯都唔get？」對自己嘅後知後覺同天真感到好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔會係最愛佢，但會因為無一齊過而有更多幻想，ff下嗰陣如果大膽啲醒目啲會點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但要分清楚，你掛住同鐘意嗰個係以前嘅佢，現在嘅佢已經係另一個人。<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">唔好話我唔提你然後懵盛盛隔十幾廿年走去搵返人，再比人當你痴線佬</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76741bf727134431f1feede831509b95dc6fc8f","tid":2331946,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"咩位？骨灰龕位？"},{"pid":"28a855f5269b1a8afa6a735ea9635fb87078a76e","tid":2331946,"uid":64701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"命定論真係好On9"},{"pid":"d57620d23710df5b4822d30e0af35e044f318121","tid":2331946,"uid":154409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"我隔咗七年再見番就一齊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a441a6835b0e8c1a7a866a7c6a25018cc6bbf07","tid":2331946,"uid":383599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d57620d23710df5b4822d30e0af35e044f318121","tid":2331946,"uid":154409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"我隔咗七年再見番就一齊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T08:40:53.000Z","msg":"都識有d朋友係咁，好浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hk